Package com.snamp.adapters

An infrastructure for writing custom SNAMP adapters.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Adapter
    Represents hosting adapter, that exposes management information to the outside world.
    AttributesRegistry
    Represents utility interface for connecting and reading management attributes.
    AttributesRegistryReader
    Represents utility interface for easy reading of connected attributes.
    AttributesRegistryWriter
    Represents utility interface for connecting attributes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAdapter
    Represents an abstract class for building adapters.
    AbstractAttributesRegistry
    Represents registry of exposed attributes based on attribute namespace.
    AttributeValue<T extends AttributeTypeInfo>
    Represents utility class that represents raw attribute value and its type.
    ConnectedAttributes
    Represents a map of exposed attributes to the adapter.
    EmbeddedAdapter  
    RestAdapterService  
    SnmpAdapterBase
    Represents a base class for SNMP adapter.
